    "However, the time information of the signal is lost after the transformation.",
    "FFT features have been shown to be effective for artifact detection 52, and we use FFT to calculate the energy of the high-frequency parts of the signal (frequencies above 80 Hz), with the intuition that high energy in the high-frequency parts of the signal should be considered as not originating from the brain.",
    "For the DWT, instead, we use the same method as described in the feature extraction paragraph for seizures here above.",
    "Even though the FFT and DWT features can be used alone and give good metrics, relying on a combination of FFT and DWT features yields the best results.",
    "After the feature extraction based on FFT and DWT, we utilize the TPOT 53 for model selection and optimization."
  ],
